About Perceptron
Perceptron is a global metrology equipment and solutions company with over 30 years of experience and the market leader in laser-based metrology and its application.
Measurement solutions for in-line and near-line dimensional gauging, CMM measurement, 3D scanning, robot guidance, gap & flush measurement and wheel alignment.
 More Details → 



 




COORD3 CMM Portfolio
Manufacturers around the world rely on COORD3 Metrology CMM solutions to measure, certify and improve the quality of their products. Click the button below to see our entire portfolio of CMM products.
 More Details → 


 



TouchDMIS – Simple CMM Software
TouchDMIS has been ergonomically designed to provide maximum productivity for both novice and expert users. TouchCloud is seamlessly integrated into TouchDMIS, allowing fast and efficient programming with accurate feature extraction from the generated point cloud and enables the user to automatically switch between tactile and laser measurements. The hybrid solution is perfect for production, prototype or first article inspection.
Brilliantly Simple And Affordable
 


 



AutoScan RoboGauge Launched
AutoScan RoboGauge combines Perceptron’s Helix 3D laser scanning sensor with industrial robot technology creating a production-floor gauging cell.
Fast | Accurate | Flexible | Robust | Collaborative
 More Details → 
 


 



AutoScan Collaborative Gauge
The latest in automated metrology products combining Collaborative Robot technology with Perceptron’s revolutionary Helix Smart Scanning Sensor technology.
 More Details → 



 




Scalable Solutions to Fit Your Application
Perceptron is uniquely positioned to offer a full spectrum of products and turnkey solutions to meet your specific metrology requirements and financial budget. Our global teams engineer custom solutions backed by our corporate resources to improve, optimize or expand your current product manufacturing process.
 More Details → 


 



Helix – Get More Information
The Helix platform offers a revolutionary laser scanning sensor that allows faster and more precise measurement of complex geometries. The unique, patented Helix technology scans parts with stationary sensors by utilizing its internal MEMS technology. This provides fully programmable line length, density and sweep-scan field of measurement.
 More Details → 


 



GD&T – Validate to Design Intent
Perceptron leverages 3D design data to provide real-time Geometric Dimensioning & Tolerancing (GD&T) information that can be applied to any production part or assembly. All measurement calculations are integral, repeatable and traceable to ANSI & ISO Standards.


 



Configure to CAD – Measure Sooner
Fully utilizing CAD data, Perceptron can deliver engineered measurement solutions faster and more efficiently. 3D data from your plant and product design can be utilized for robot reach studies and robot path programming before your first assembly is built.


 



Global Solutions, Local Support
Our customers are global and demand mission-critical production metrology solutions with local support. Uniquely, Perceptron owns support locations in 15 countries.
 More Details → 


 







