Software Development Engineer – Plymouth, MI
As a Perceptron Software Development Engineer, you will be part of a team to develop and test cutting-edge software solutions for our customers in both the metrology and in-line measurement domains.
The Software Development Engineer duties include:

Full engagement in development cycles across Perceptron software products
Contribute to a team of Engineers to produce high quality metrology system products

Candidate must have / be:

Strong C++, C#, OO design & analysis (UML, Design Patterns)
Expert in multi-thread, real time system
Minimum two years of experience in software development
Solid written and verbal communication skills
Familiar with version control, bug tracking
Enjoy hands-on engineering development
Team player with good interpersonal skills

